                  "revisionId": 2656298,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Mutually exclusive with Thunderbolt (cannot be equipped together)."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Mending Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488115,
                  "revisionId": 2656298,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Though having AoE capabilities, the Ferrox and Scourge spearguns can equip this mod. They also have different interactions with Health orbs:"
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Mending Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488115,
                  "revisionId": 2656298,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Primary fire's beam/projectiles and their AoE explosions will pick up orbs."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Mending Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488115,
                  "revisionId": 2656298,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Secondary fire will also pick up orbs if:"
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Mending Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488115,
                  "revisionId": 2656298,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The speargun hits the orb directly, which will make the weapon return to the player immediately, as if their timer had expired when deployed."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Mending Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488115,
                  "revisionId": 2656298,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The Health orbs are within the Scourge 's radial explosion, but not the Ferrox 's AoE."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Mending Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488115,
                  "revisionId": 2656298,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "This mod will make projectiles stop when hitting Health orbs, potentially wasting ammo. This can vary with hitscan weapons."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Mending Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488115,
                  "revisionId": 2656298,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Weapons with Multishot can pick up Health orbs with just a single projectile."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Mending Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488115,
                  "revisionId": 2656298,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Health orbs picked up this way will trigger on-Health-pickup effects, like Arcane Pulse , Health Conversion and Equilibrium ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Mending Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488115,
                  "revisionId": 2656298,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Equilibrium (including Equinox 's passive) does not scale off of the increased health gained."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Mending Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488115,
                  "revisionId": 2656298,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Bonus does affect Equilibrium 's conversion on Health Orbs from dispensers in Arena gamemodes."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Mending Shot",
                  "pageId": 1488115,
                  "revisionId": 2656298,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Increased Health Orb Effectiveness is additive with similar increases from Amber Archon Shard and Restorative Bond , but multiplicative with Dagath 's Passive."
                }
              },
